Blackstone’s Valad Plans to Expand in Finland, Kauppalehti Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-14T05:32:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/blackstone-s-valad-plans-to-expand-in-finland-kauppalehti-says.html
Blackstone Group LP (BX) ’s Valad Property
Group plans to expand real estate purchases in  Finland , Risto
Linnankoski, Valad’s local head of asset management, told
newspaper Kauppalehti in an interview.  “We’re seeking properties to buy,” Linnankoski said
according to Helsinki-based Kauppalehti. “We’re looking for
multi-user real estate outside of city centers and properties we
can transform to add value.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  